# ShopMecko — Auto Marketplace Platform

A multi-sided marketplace connecting **Car Owners**, **Car Repairers**, and **Spare Parts Sellers**, managed by an **Admin**.

---

## Overview

**ShopMecko** is a full-stack web application built with Next.js (App Router), styled with Vanilla CSS, and powered by Supabase for auth, database, and real-time features. The platform brings together the auto repair ecosystem in one unified experience.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a significant full-stack project. The plan uses **Supabase** (free tier available) for the backend. You will need to create a free Supabase project at [supabase.com](https://supabase.com) and provide the API keys. We can scaffold everything and add keys after.

> [!WARNING]
> Real-time chat requires Supabase Realtime (included in Supabase free tier). Location-based repairer search will use a browser Geolocation API + coordinates stored in Supabase — no paid map API needed for MVP.

> [!NOTE]
> Phase 1 (this plan) covers the full working MVP. Payment processing (e.g., Stripe) is noted as a future enhancement and is NOT included in this plan.

