### Database Schema (Supabase PostgreSQL)

#### Users & Profiles
```sql
-- profiles table (extends Supabase auth.users)
profiles {
  id: uuid (FK auth.users)
  role: enum('car_owner', 'repairer', 'parts_seller', 'admin')
  full_name: text
  phone: text
  avatar_url: text
  bio: text
  address: text
  city: text
  state: text
  latitude: float
  longitude: float
  created_at: timestamptz
}

-- repairer_details (extra info for repairers)
repairer_details {
  id: uuid (FK profiles)
  specializations: text[]
  years_experience: int
  rating: float
  total_reviews: int
  is_available: bool
  workshop_name: text
  workshop_images: text[]
  hourly_rate: numeric
}
```

#### Spare Parts Marketplace
```sql
-- products
products {
  id: uuid
  seller_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  name: text
  description: text
  price: numeric
  stock_quantity: int
  category: text
  brand: text
  compatible_cars: text[]
  images: text[]
  is_active: bool
  created_at: timestamptz
}

-- orders
orders {
  id: uuid
  buyer_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  seller_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  product_id: uuid (FK products)
  quantity: int
  total_price: numeric
  status: enum('pending','confirmed','shipped','delivered','cancelled')
  delivery_address: text
  created_at: timestamptz
}
```

#### Chat & Messaging
```sql
-- conversations
conversations {
  id: uuid
  participant_1: uuid (FK profiles)
  participant_2: uuid (FK profiles)
  created_at: timestamptz
}

-- messages
messages {
  id: uuid
  conversation_id: uuid (FK conversations)
  sender_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  content: text
  is_read: bool
  created_at: timestamptz
}
```

#### Reviews
```sql
-- reviews
reviews {
  id: uuid
  repairer_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  reviewer_id: uuid (FK profiles)
  rating: int (1–5)
  comment: text
  created_at: timestamptz
}
```

