### Pages & Features

#### [NEW] Landing Page (`app/page.tsx`)
- Hero section with clear value proposition
- "Find a Repairer Near You" search bar
- Feature highlights for all 3 user types
- Marketplace preview
- Top-rated repairers showcase
- CTA to register

#### [NEW] Authentication (`app/(auth)/`)
- Unified login/register page
- **Role selection** on sign-up: Car Owner / Repairer / Parts Seller
- Profile completion flow after registration

#### [NEW] Role-Based Dashboards (`app/(dashboard)/dashboard/`)
- **Car Owner Dashboard**: Nearby repairers, recent orders, active chats, service history
- **Repairer Dashboard**: Incoming service requests, recent chats, order history, profile stats, rating
- **Parts Seller Dashboard**: Product listings, order management, revenue summary, analytics
- **Admin Dashboard**: All users, product approvals, order overview, reported content

#### [NEW] Marketplace (`app/marketplace/`)
- Product grid with filters (category, brand, price range, compatible car)
- Product detail page
- Add to cart → Place order flow
- Seller profile link on each product

#### [NEW] Repairer Search (`app/repairers/`)
- Search by city/area or use current location
- Filter by specialization, rating, availability
- Repairer cards with rating, distance, hourly rate
- Repairer detail page with full profile, reviews, gallery

#### [NEW] Profile Pages
- Public profile for repairers and sellers
- Edit profile (avatar upload, bio, specializations, location)
- Repairer: show reviews, gallery, availability toggle

#### [NEW] Chat System (`app/(dashboard)/chat/`)
- Conversation list with unread counts
- Real-time messaging (Supabase Realtime)
- Start chat from repairer profile or seller profile

#### [NEW] Orders (`app/(dashboard)/orders/`)
- Order history for buyers (car owners + repairers)
- Order management for sellers (confirm, ship, deliver)
- Order detail view with status timeline

#### [NEW] Admin Panel (`app/admin/`)
- User management (list, view, suspend)
- Product management (approve, reject, remove)
- Order overview
- Platform statistics

#### [NEW] Core UI Components (`components/ui/`)
- Button, Input, Card, Badge, Modal, Dropdown
- Avatar, Rating Stars, Loader, Toast notifications
- Search Bar, Filter Panel
- Navigation (Navbar + Sidebar)

